list.abstract: 仓木麻衣34th SL的C/W曲 是来自日本最著名的歌手之一。Kuraki自从看过一部关于MichaelJackson的生活电影和惠特尼休斯顿的音乐会后就梦想成为一名歌手。自99年「Love,DayAfterTomorror」后推出的「DeliciousWay」，获得了2000年度细碟销量冠军、大碟销量亚军、最佳作词、最出色新人奖和最高唱片收入亚军等五个奖项，并打破了原来的R&B小天后宇多田光的纪录，和滨崎步并列第一（总销量第二），出道不到一年就被公认为唯一可以威胁另外两大天后的新天后。
《Anywhere》是Rita Ora演唱的一首歌曲，由Brian D Lee、Rita Sahatçiu Ora、Nick Gale、Alexandra Tamposi、Alessandro Lindblad、Nolan Lambroza、Andrew Wotman作曲，于2018年11月23日发行。

yingyinNormal.en: You can do anything, go anywhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你可以做任何事，去任何地方。

yingyinNormal.en: Microbots can move anything, anywhere, with ease.
yingyinNormal.zh: 微型机器人，可以轻松移动任何物体至任何地方。

yingyinNormal.en: From Circular Quay you can get just about anywhere by ferry, water taxi or train.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在环形码头，您可以乘坐渡轮，水上的士或火车到达任何地方。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, but he never drive anyone anywhere. He's practically losing the front seat of that car.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，你知道的，他从不载任何人去任何地方，他简直就是丢了那车的前座。

yingyinNormal.en: Its economy is the largest on earth and it makes and exports more goods than anywhere else on the globe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 中国是地球上的最大的经济体，生产和出口的商品比全球其它任何地方都多。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, melodramatic? Anything I do, anywhere I go, if I go on job interview, if I go on a date, they Google me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小题大做？我做任何事，去任何地方，无论面试还是约会，对方都会上谷歌搜索我。

yingyinNormal.en: I can slip in and out, anywhere I like, you know. When I get the urge. HH Holmes. Murder Castle. But done right.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我可以随意出入我想去的任何地方，当我犯瘾时。HH·霍姆斯。谋杀城堡。但做得更好。

yingyinNormal.en: Recovered from the scene of the firefight in the desert. Not sold anywhere commercially in the world, even black market. So?
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是在沙漠里的那场交火中发现的，从未在世界上的任何地方出售过，连黑市都没有。所以呢？

yingyinNormal.en: But doesn't it need railway tracks to run on? Oh no. I've fitted Gertrude with car wheels, so she can go anywhere she likes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可是火车不是需要铁轨才能运行吗？噢，不需要，我给格特鲁德装上轮子就行啦，这样她就可以去任何地方啦。

yingyinNormal.en: Let me put it to you this way. It took us nearly a decade to find Osama Bin Laden. With this, we could locate him anywhere on the planet in a couple of hours.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我这么跟你说吧，我们花了将近十年才找到本·拉登，但有了这装备，我们在几小时之内就能在这个星球的任何地方找到他。

yingyinNormal.en: I don't want to go anywhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我哪也不想去。

yingyinNormal.en: I checked anywhere a good boy might go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已经都找过了你还知道他会去哪么。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, I'll see if I can get anywhere in court.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那行，我去和法院打招呼。

yingyinNormal.en: No way, han. That man could've overdosed anywhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没门 Han，他在随处都可能嗑蕴药过量。

yingyinNormal.en: And, for the first time anywhere, Scarlet Overkill!
yingyinNormal.zh: 以及，首次亮相的，斯嘉丽·杀人狂!

yingyinNormal.en: There's no system quite like this anywhere in the world.
yingyinNormal.zh: 再没有像这个国家的系统一样的了。

yingyinNormal.en: He's not going anywhere, Finch. His key no longer works.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他走不了，芬奇，他的钥匙不管用了。

yingyinNormal.en: You are not going anywhere, Thorin. You're going to live.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你哪都不会去，索林，你会活下去的。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies》

yingyinNormal.en: Sounds like you have company. They're not going anywhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 听起来你好象有客人。他们总在。

yingyinNormal.en: It's absolutely Alice. You're absolutely Alice. I'd know you anywhere. I'd know him anywhere.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她就是那个爱丽丝，你就是那个爱丽丝，无论如何，我也认得你，无论如何我也认得她。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: It has not gotten <highlight>anywhere</highlight> close to that, and one big reason is sticker shock.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 它还没有接近那个水平，一个重要的原因是价格冲击。

examination_example.sentence: Our mental health doesn't really go <highlight>anywhere</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们的心理健康其实一直都在。

examination_example.sentence: This is the credibility process, through which the individual researcher's me, here, now becomes the community's anyone, <highlight>anywhere</highlight>, anytime.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这就是可信性过程，通过这个过程，在这里，个体研究者的“我”现在变成了社区中的“任何人”、“任何地点”以及“任何时间”。

examination_example.sentence: Practically everyone can make and receive calls <highlight>anywhere</highlight>, anytime.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 几乎每个人都可以随时随地拨打和接听电话。

examination_example.sentence: Most important, I have learned that fathers don't need clones in footsteps or <highlight>anywhere</highlight> else.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 最重要的是，我了解到父亲不需要克隆人的足迹或其他任何地方。

examination_example.sentence: There were great civilizations, splendid empires, but no freedom <highlight>anywhere</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这里有伟大的文明，辉煌的帝国，但哪里都没有自由。

examination_example.sentence: Do this and you'll be welcome <highlight>anywhere</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这样做，你在任何地方都会受到欢迎。
他在任何地方都找不到他的幸福。

examination_example.sentence: "I started to think that it was possible to have an adventure <highlight>anywhere</highlight>."
examination_example.sentence_trans: "我开始认为在任何地方进行冒险都是可能的。"

examination_example.sentence: If you turn the park into a golf course, these kids won't have <highlight>anywhere</highlight> to go.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果你把公园变成高尔夫球场，这些孩子将无处可去。

examination_example.sentence: They think public traffic in China is very fast and cheap, which can take them <highlight>anywhere</highlight> easily.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们认为中国的公共交通非常快捷和便宜，可以很容易地把他们带到任何地方。

examination_example.sentence: That is, <highlight>anywhere</highlight> from 250 billion to 500 billion "earths".
examination_example.sentence_trans: 也就是说，任何地方从2500亿到5000亿个“地球”。

word_usage.usage:
当形容词修饰复合不定副词somewhere, anywhere, nowhere, everywhere 时，形容词要后置。
如：My grandfather wanted to move somewhere quiet.
我爷爷想搬到安静的地方去住。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 表示“在某个地方”，通常用在肯定句中。
表示“在某个地方”时，通常用在否定句或疑问句中；还可以表示“在任何地方”，此时可以用在肯定句中。
